      "rationale": "Literature review confirms linear-elastic Ti-6Al-4V behavior is appropriate below yield for the load levels of interest. Frictional contact (μ=0.3) at screw-rod interface is supported by published tribological data. Sensitivity analysis demonstrates QoI insensitivity to ±20% friction coefficient variation. Model form uncertainty estimated at 3.2% and incorporated in E/uval calculation. Gradation 3 achieved."
